column6: Out of the fire, and into the frying pan. Or, more precisely, out of spaceship full of pirate killers and into the alien jungle filled with giant hungry space monsters! Cyclops and Corsair are reunited at last, but will they survive long enough to survive their touching reunion? Oh, and what's that strange ticking noise? Could it be coming from the nearby superweapon capable of DESTROYING ENTIRE GALAXIES?
column8: | artist:Javier Garron | writer:John Layman | penciller (cover):Alexander Lozano
